{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_02_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 撮影ごっこ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースの沖縄ライブ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the end of the Sunny Peace Okinawa concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げのバーベキューの準備まで\n手伝ってもらって悪いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s good of you to even help with\npreparations for the after-show barbecue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "かまへんよ、パーティの準備は嫌いやないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind‚ it’s not like I hate party preparations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 10.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても鈴村さんの別荘の側にビーチがあるとはな\nおかげで沖縄の海を眺めながらバーベキューが出来るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having a beach right next to your family’s holiday villa\nmeans we can have our barbecue with a view of Okinawa’s sea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 20.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ここやったら誰も来ないし\nみんなも人目を気にせずに騒げるやろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nobody else comes here‚\nso everyone can get wild without worrying about people seeing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "この場所を提供したうちにもっと感謝してもええんやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind if you’re even more grateful for me providing this place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、鈴村さんには頭が上がらないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ I have to take my hat off to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今日の機材トラブルも鈴村さんのおかげで乗り切れた\nおかげでライブは大成功だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And thanks to you‚ we were able to get past today’s equipment trouble.\nThe concert was a big success‚ with your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちはたいしたことしてへんよ\nライブが盛り上がったんはサニピの実力やん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t do anything special.\nIt was Sunny Peace’s skills that made the show such a hit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 47.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "サニピは夏の太陽みたいに笑顔が眩しくて\n沖縄が似合うええグループやな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace has bright smiles like the summer sun.\nThey’re a great fit as a group for Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "野外ライブで盛り上がる会場を見てたら\nうちも歌いたくなってたまらんかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking out at the venue getting so pumped up by the outdoor show‚\nI wanted to sing so much‚ I couldn’t stand it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 61.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、次に沖縄でイベントがある時は\nTRINITYAiLEを参加させてくれへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So next time there’s an event in Okinawa‚\nwon’t you let TRINITYAiLE join in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらうちらがサニピ以上のライブを披露したるで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you do that‚ we’ll bring a live show to top Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 72.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それを見て今度はサニピが刺激を受ける訳か\n刺激して高めあえる相手が身近にいるのはいいことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And watching your show‚ it’ll be good stimulus for Sunny Peace.\nIt’s good to have people close by‚ so you can spur each other to get better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "良きライバルでいてくれて\n俺達はトリエルに感謝しなくちゃいけないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re grateful to have TRINITYAiLE\nas our good rivals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 86.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "……感謝するんはうちの方や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re the ones who should be grateful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルが移籍前と変わらず、いい仕事が出来てるんは\n星見プロのおかげやし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can do a good job‚ just like we did before we transferred.\nThat’s thanks to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 95.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "いいライバルにいいマネージャー……\nうちらが星見プロを選んだんは間違いちゃうかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A good manager and good rivals…\nChoosing Hoshimi Productions was a great decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 102.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの一員になれてほんまによかったわ\n瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんもきっとそう思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so glad I can be part of Hoshimi Productions.\nI’m sure Rui and Sumire think the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nこれからもうちらをよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nPlease keep on looking out for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 116.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "……あはは。なんや柄にもないこと言うてしもたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Listen to me‚ I never talk like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "しばらく瑠依ちゃん達と会ってへんから\n調子狂ってしもたんかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven’t seen Rui and Sumire in a while.\nIs that why I’m not myself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはいつも三人一緒だったからな\n二人に会えなくて寂しいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You three of TRINITYAiLE are always together.\nAre you lonely for not seeing them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 133.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "せやね……早く二人に会いたいわ\n瑠依ちゃん達、今頃何してるんやろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I want to see them as soon as possible.\nI wonder what they’re doing now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "気になるなら連絡してみたらどうだ？\n沖縄の写真を送ればいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re worried‚ why not contact them?\nHow about you send them a photo from Okinawa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 147.16666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "写真かぁ……せやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A photo… Good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 151.73333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "それやったら一度やってみたかったことがあんねんけど\nちょっと手伝ってくれへん？",
